00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:42,344
Two people investigated the same swamp... and never spoke to each other about it. Nella captured Ligators for reasons she kept to herself, tracking the creatures' strange growth with the focused calm of someone who had suspected this moment was coming. JM shouted his findings at anyone who would listen... which meant no one with authority listened at all. The swamp did not care about either of them. Deep in the water... something OLDER and LARGER than a Ligator had made itself at home... and the walls of Kerning City... above and below ground... were already beginning to feel its presence.
